    <body>
        <p>To add question feedback, select the <span class="Bold">Feedback</span> tab.<ul><li>To add feedback for a correct answer, enter the text in the <span class="Italic">Question has been answered correctly</span> feedback area.</li><li>To add feedback for an incorrect answer, enter the text in the <span class="Italic">Answer was wrong</span> feedback area.</li><li>To add feedback for specific responses, click <span class="Bold">Add new feedback</span> at the bottom of the page.<ol style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;" class="Gotham"><li>Set the conditions. Select <span class="Bold">Score</span> or <span class="Bold">Response</span>.<ul><li>If score is selected, select the <span class="Bold">operator</span> ( =, &gt;, &gt;=, &lt;, &lt;=) and set the <span class="Bold">score value</span>. </li><li>If response is selected, select the <span class="Bold">operator</span> (=, !=) and select the <span class="Bold">answer</span>.</li></ul></li><li>To add another condition, click <img src="../../../Graphics/TA/Icon-AddFeedbackCondition.png" class="Inline30px" alt="Add Condition" title="Add Condition" />. To remove the condition, click <img src="../../../Graphics/TA/Icon-RemoveFeedbackCondition.png" class="Inline30px" alt="Remove Condition" title="Remove Condition" />.<div class="Note" MadCap:autonum="&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: 'Montserrat';&quot; class=&quot;mcFormatFamily&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #00a69c;&quot; class=&quot;mcFormatColor&quot;&gt;NOTE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;"><p>The same feedback is displayed for multiple conditions. To add separate feedback text for each condition you must add a new feedback.</p></div></li><li>Enter the feedback text for the condition in the area provided.</li><li>To add feedback for another condition, click <span class="Bold">Add a new feedback</span> and repeat the steps above.</li><li>To remove individual feedback, click <span class="Bold">Delete</span> to left of the feedback area.</li></ol></li></ul></p>
    </body>
